The new tanks will be of a worse type (the gunners will have to leave the armoured cabin and carry the ammunition by hand without protection).
The cars - Toyota Hilux - are new and good
Trucks and various armored vehicles - at a decent level, moreover, it has already been possible to get rid of the Praga V3S even in specialist units.
Airplanes: combat - decent, but at the end of their rental, transport - too small with a short range, but modern.
Drones - few and only small types with no combat potential
Missiles - we don't have any (but we produce them and export them abroad)
NGO: mid-Cold War, obsolete; short-range - good, modern, relatively good numbers.
