The state, responsible for the purchase and distribution of face masks, masks and respirators to the professions closest to the coronavirus, has spent billions of crowns in recent weeks on their procurement.
The iRozhlas server compared the purchases of individual ministries and found that during a single day the amounts for respirators differed by hundreds of crowns.
