Chilling footage shows the moment a terrified monkey cowered in a toilet before its heartless owner flushed her down and laughed.
Holland also fed the monkeys sausages, kebabs and hamburgers, regardless of their actual nutritional needs.
Gwent Magistrates Court has now banned her from keeping animals for life, The Sun reports.
